title: GTA+
headline: GTA+
subtitle: This Month’s Benefits
content:
In addition to the recurring monthly GTA$500,000 deposited directly into your Maze Bank account, GTA+ Members who've signed up for this month (November 6 - December 8) will also receive:

— The Enus Paragon S (Sports)
— 50% off Arcade Properties
— 50% off the Buckingham Luxor Deluxe (Plane)
— 50% off the Buckingham Swift Deluxe (Helicopter)
— And more

Membership automatically renews monthly, cancel anytime. Visit rsg.ms/gtaplus for more info.
